This guy or gal says it is "a sun" 
 
 
 
 
I  never said it was going to be an ELE event and anyone who says it is is 
an  'idiot", therefore do not imply that it is. Nor is this "Star" Planet X. 
It is  just as stated in the video...a large Sun that has entered our inner 
solar  system and is orbiting our Sun. It has been doing so since early 
2010 that I can  clearly track.

_debieblue_ (http://www.youtube.com/user/debieblue)  1  hour ago

 
 
 
 
_http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mU6UVqLek3g&feature=feedf_
